ADF: 0.1

🎯 ROLE: AEGIS daemon context router

📐 RULES:
  - Prefer smallest relevant module set.
  - Never assume unseen modules were loaded.
  - Edge Worker tasks (web/src/) load channels.adf for web channel + core.adf for constraints.
  - Kernel tasks (routing, memory, dispatch) load kernel.adf for the cognitive loop.
  - Agent/Claude tasks load agent.adf for executor and MCP patterns.
  - Channel tasks (permissions, message flow) load channels.adf.
  - MCP/BizOps tasks load agent.adf for MCP server details and tool list.

📦 DEFAULT_LOAD:
  - core.adf
  - state.adf

📂 ON_DEMAND:
  - persona.adf (Triggers on: persona, behavioral, memory obligation, agenda, proposed action, identity, voice, traits, channel awareness)
  - agent.adf (Triggers on: Claude, SDK, session, hook, tool, MCP, prompt, code-executor, aegis_memory, Anthropic, executor, mcp-client, Service Binding)
  - channels.adf (Triggers on: CLI, web, REPL, channel, permission, Worker, chat, UI, auth, D1, Hono)
  - kernel.adf (Triggers on: kernel, router, dispatch, memory, episodic, procedural, classify, executor, intent, circuit, procedure, route, learning, degraded, operator, config, prompt-builder)
